data.description: The Townhouse you have been waiting for at Raintree (largest Sonoma model). Desirable Corner unit with lots of natural lighting. 3/2.5 with loft easily convertible to a 4th bedroom, Laundry room, 2nd floor balcony, covered Patio. Fully upgraded Quartz countertops throughout, Glass Shower, Stainless Steel Appliances with Convection Ovens. The latest on Brand New Laminate flooring 3 months old, Brand New California Closets just installed including Pantry and Laundry room, Hunter Douglas Motorized Shades on the first floor and primary bedroom, 4 Ring Security Cameras, Smart Thermostat, 2 Car Garage with Overhead Storage. Clubhouse and mailboxes across the street with plenty visitor parking.Centrally located with lots of shopping and restaurants near by,easy access to the I-75 and FL Turnpike.
